 Take Twitter or other microblogging platforms as an example, such interactions
 may include tweets about the firm, and the corresponding retweets, comments,
 and likes.
 The volume of interactions can be measured as the overall level or the
 increment during certain period of time (e.g., the launch of a new product
 by the firm).
 
\end_layout

